title: WeWow Back to School - Day 5: The Science of Awe
description:
Welcome back to Back to School Week at WeWow! Today, we're listening to "The Science of Awe" and making egg shells disappear right before our eyes! Tinker with today's tinkering challenge and share your findings with us at tinkercast.com/share! Want to catch up on other daily tinkering challenges? Head over to the WeWow podcast feed where you get your podcasts and click subscribe!
